WEBVTT

00:00.272 --> 00:01.705
Previously, on Beyond...

00:01.740 --> 00:02.906
While you were in your coma

00:02.941 --> 00:05.001
your mind traveled to another world.

00:05.001 --> 00:06.676
This is where we met.
I call it The Realm.

00:06.712 --> 00:08.778
Am I the first girl to be brought
up to your bedroom?

00:08.814 --> 00:10.981
One of the gazillion things
I missed was...

00:11.016 --> 00:12.716
hanging out with girls.

00:12.751 --> 00:15.151
Hollow Sky has been involved
in youth-based charities.

00:15.187 --> 00:16.786
Fort Reed Helping Hands.

00:16.822 --> 00:18.822
It's run by Pastor Ian Brachman.

00:18.857 --> 00:20.390
Our son's friend was murdered.

00:20.425 --> 00:23.059
Now, I'm not saying that this Hollow
Sky was directly responsible,

00:23.095 --> 00:24.794
but there's got to be a connection.

00:24.830 --> 00:25.829
I'll see what I can do.

00:25.864 --> 00:28.798
Charlie Singer? I wanna help you.

00:28.834 --> 00:29.866
Mm-mm.

00:29.902 --> 00:31.968
I need something from you first.

00:32.003 --> 00:34.137
It's not her! It's not your mother.

00:34.172 --> 00:35.839
He's seeing what he wants to see.

00:35.874 --> 00:37.707
- Now what?
- Blow up the bridge.

